==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ping
<hw>Ping</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Probably of imitative
origin.]</ety> <def>The sound made by a bullet in striking a solid
object or in passing through the air.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ping</ent>⟦br⟧

